## Third-party Licenses

This project uses the following third-party services and libraries:

### OpenWeatherMap API
- Service: Weather data API
- Website: https://openweathermap.org/
- License: Data provided under OpenWeatherMap Terms of Service
- Usage: Weather information for headache risk calculation

### LINE LIFF SDK
- Library: LINE Front-end Framework SDK
- Website: https://developers.line.biz/
- License: LINE Corporation Terms of Service
- Usage: Integration with LINE messaging platform

### Tailwind CSS
- Library: CSS framework
- Website: https://tailwindcss.com/
- License: MIT License
- Usage: UI styling and responsive design

### Google Apps Script
- Platform: Google Cloud Platform
- Website: https://script.google.com/
- License: Google Cloud Platform Terms of Service
- Usage: Backend API proxy for weather data

