## Disclaimer

This application provides weather-based headache risk predictions for informational purposes only. It is not intended as medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Users should consult healthcare professionals for medical concerns.

The accuracy of weather data and headache risk calculations may vary. The developers are not responsible for any decisions made based on the information provided by this application.
